\id PHM
\h FILIMON
\toc1 Filimon
\toc2 Flm
\mt1 Filimon
\mt2 Naoa it…ôm Pol t…ôm…ôte tuw…®n k…ôm Filimon
\imt1 N…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u Filimon
\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Pol t…ôm…ôte naoa u.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm Filimon …ôp…ôh e nim…ôfak ik…®n Kolosi. Ilau fren w…®r. Filimon in et…ômim kit it…ôm tatos slef m…®n.
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* E nian …ôh, net…ômim tep…ôt koatos slef. K…ôn i…ôfak m…®n neen m…®n, ilat m…®n koatos slef m…®n. Filimon, r…ôhan kit …ôh ik…®n slef, n…ôrg…®n u, Onesimas. M…ôto Onesimas, in t…ômakl…ôh-in m…ôni neen r…ôha Filimon, k…ôn …ômun, in mag…®m. Ok…ôm…ô Filimon ot…ôplan Onesimas, lou r…ôha Rom tat…ôn m…ô Filimon t…®tun nohamnu…ôn t…®m…®s. M…ôto Onesimas t…ôm…ôplan Pol …ôp…ôh e kalapus ik…®n Rom, k…ôn Pol t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r k…ôm in, k…ôn t…ômahat…ôt…ô e Iesu Kristo. K…ôn Onesimas in t…ômasitu e Pol. K…ôn Pol t…ômahl-ip…ôn in t…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn o Filimon. Pol t…ôm…ôn k…ôm Filimon m…ôm…ô nat …ôpnap…®n Onesimas in slef r…ôhan, m…ôto roiu in pian e Iesu Kristo.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Pol t…ôm…ôte naoa u mat…ôtap…ôh o Filimon m…ôm…ô otaluin nol…ôn r…ôha Onesimas, k…ôn mos in t…®t…ôtl…®g-pa m…®n. Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô in r…ôhan slef, m…ôto Pol tolkeike m…ôm…ô Filimon ot…ôplan Onesimas tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô in pian kit e Iesu Kristo.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Io Pol, it…ôm etat…®g e kalapus o Kristo Iesu, it…®mlau pi…ôtat Timoti, iatu…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ik Filimon. Ik iol…®t…®mlau it…ôm ekioalkeike p…®k, k…ôn kit…ôhal k…ôt…ôhalol w…ôk kiti…ôh …ôm r…ôha Iesu.
\v 2 K…ôn iatu…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm w…®n…®tat Apia, ne Akipas it…ôm kitat mopael m…®n koat…ôluag…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn iatu…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ôm r…ôha nim…ôfak it…ôm koatuwa moat…ôfak e r…ôham nim…ô.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kol 4:17; 2 Tim 2:3 \x*
\v 3 P…ôs Uhg…®n u Tata r…ôhatat, ne I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo okuawte-in n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm it…ômat.
\s1 N…ôfak…ôn r…ôha Pol
\p 
\v 4 E nian m…®n rafin it…ôm iat…ôfak ron ik, mat…ôn tagkiu k…ôm Uhg…®n ron ik,
\v 5 m…ôto-inu em…ôto nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôham e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu, ne nolkeike…ôn r…ôham it…ôm tatuw…®n o n…ôfak m…®n rafin.
\v 6 K…ôn iat…ôplan nol…ôn r…ôham, m…ôm…ô natawte e n…®kim agien m…ôto-inu e r…ôham nahat…ôt…ô…ôn. K…ôn iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô nol…ôn …ôh otasitu lam m…ôm…ô on…ôk…®tun w…®r k…ôn mos nat w…®r m…®n rafin r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ôtawte-in e Kristo k…ôm kitat.
\v 7 Piak, iat…ôfak n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu r…ôham nolkeike…ôn t…ômol n…®ki n…ôfak m…®n koat…ôto t…ôw…®r, k…ôn nian em…ôto, io m…®n, n…®kik t…ômagien k…ôn tat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn lan.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt 2 Kor 7:4 \x*
\s1 N…ôtap…ôh…ôn r…ôha Pol
\p 
\v 8 Tol n…ôhlan, e Kristo es…ôg…®n…ôn o n…ôn…ôn k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô on…ôkol nat kit it…ôm n…ôk…ôike mol,
\v 9 m…ôto esol mihin…ôn. Iat…ôtap…ôh-in …ôm e nolkeike…ôn. Io iagu…®hl kit, etat…®g e kalapus o Kristo Iesu. K…ôn io inu Pol,
\v 10 iat…ôtap…ôh-in suah kit ron ik e r…ôhak n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô nakos e n…®kim agien. Suah …ôh in t…ômuwa tahmen-p…ôn e n…ôt…®k nian em…ôtat…®g e kalapus, inu Onesimas, r…ôham slef.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Kor 4:15; Kol 4:9 \x*
\v 11 Aup…ôn ik…®n, in t…ôm…ôsol w…ôk w…®r…ôn k…ôm ik, m…ôto roiu in t…®tun nol…ôn w…ôk t…ôw…®r k…ôm kilau k…ôr…ôn.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft N…ôrg…®n u ‚ÄúOnesimas‚Äù in t…ôm…ô, ‚Äúet…ôm it…ôm t…®tun nol…ôn w…ôk w…®r.‚Äù\f*
\p 
\v 12 K…ôn roiu, etahl-ip…®n…ô m…®n suah u, et…ôm it…ôm iakolkeike p…®k.
\v 13 Ok…ôm…ô t…ôtat…®g it…®mlau min, n…®kik tagien ron, k…ôn in otatos n…ômeem m…ôtasitu lak nian etat…®g ik…®n-u e kalapus o namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r.
\v 14 M…ôto esolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô ekol nat kit it…ôm ik n…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn. K…ôn ok…ôm…ô natol nat w…®r, iakolkeike m…ôm…ô in tat…®s…®-p…ôn …ôm e n…®kim agien, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô nat io iat…ôk…ôike k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô nakol.
\p 
\v 15 Es…®tun…ôn, ok…ôm-naka Onesimas t…ômag…®m e nian …ôku…ôk…®r u m…ôm…ô onakos m…®n in t…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n n…ôtuat…®g ag…®n-…ôh,
\v 16 m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô in otol m…®n …ôm slef r…ôham, k…ôp. M…ôto roiu …ôh, in suah w…®r tapr…ôk…®s-in slef kit, in pialau et…ôm t…ôw…®r. Io iakoleike p…®k in, m…ôto ik onakolkeike p…®k in tapr…ôk…®s, m…ôto-inu in r…ôham slef, k…ôn in piam e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Tim 6:2 \x*
\p 
\v 17 Nakatehm io m…ôm…ô k…ômuea kiti…ôh e w…ôk ne nolkeike…ôn r…ôha Kristo, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, iat…ôtap…ôh m…ôm…ô nian in ot…®mn…ô, nakos in e n…®kim agien tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô io.
\v 18 Ok…ôm…ô t…ômol nat kit t…ôrat k…ôm ik, o t…ômos r…ôham nat kit k…ôn m…ôs…ôtou…ôn, p…ôs n…ôk…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn t…ôtat…®g e kaon r…ôhak.
\v 19 K…ôn …ôh-roiu, Io Pol, iat…ôte e nelm…ôk \it ‚Äî p…ôs io epan…ôtou.\it* M…ôto t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô n…ôsaluin…ôn r…ôham kaon asol ag…®n k…ôm io, it…ôm tol min-nulan, emasitu lam k…ôn n…ômos r…ôham n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.
\v 20 Piak, iakolkeike m…ôm…ô onak…ôtuoun mat…ôtou r…ôham kaon\f + \fr 1:20 \ft E n…ôghat…ôn Kris, n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol ik…®n-u ‚Äúm…ôtou r…ôham kaon‚Äù in iu…ôhk…®r …ôm e n…ôrg…® Onesimas.\f* k…ôm io, k…ôn ol nat u iat…ôtap…ôh-in e n…ôrg…® I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôn ol n…®kik tat…ôto t…ôw…®r e Kristo.
\v 21 Iat…ôte naoa u k…ôm ik m…ôto-inu ek…®tun m…ôm…ô on…ôkol n…ôwiak, k…ôn on…ôkol tapr…ôk…®s-in nat naka it…ôm iat…ôtap…ôh-in.
\p 
\v 22 K…ôn nat kit m…®n, af…ôl r…ôhak kit rum m…ôto-inu em…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn e Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô in otos io ek…®t…ôl…®g-p…®n…ô m…®n ot…ômat, inu noa n…ôfak…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Fil 1:25; 2:24 \x*
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol
\p 
\v 23 Epafras, it…®mlau min etuat…®g e kalapus o n…ôrg…® Kristo Iesu, k…ôn in tat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Kol 1:7 \x*
\v 24 K…ôn Mak, ne Aristakas, ne Temas, ne Luk, it…ôm it…®mat ekoatol w…ôk kiti…ôh, ilat m…®n koat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat.\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Kol 4:10-14 \x*
\p 
\v 25 P…ôs I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu Kristo otawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm it…ômat rafin. 
